input.sentences: i was sad when my father put my childhood home up for sale . i had a lot of fond memories of the kitchen .
i shared my room with my many older brothers .
the living room did n't look familiar at all when i went to get a final look at it . all the furniture had been moved out .
the outside itself looked smaller than i remember .
i did see the table bench that i helped my father made . so many good memories at that house .
